	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Family BASIC is just NROM plus battery-backed RAM; you should be able to use the Kazzo to program flash on NROM.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

